275
00:22:42.815 --> 00:22:43.945
Sa Ho Sung.

276
00:22:44.015 --> 00:22:45.384
Try harder next time.

277
00:22:46.255 --> 00:22:48.884
- Ji Won. - What?

278
00:22:49.985 --> 00:22:51.055
It's nothing.

279
00:22:51.824 --> 00:22:53.555
Do you want to see Mi Dal?

280
00:22:53.555 --> 00:22:54.965
Not at all.

281
00:22:54.965 --> 00:22:56.525
What do you mean?

282
00:22:57.695 --> 00:22:58.695
Yes.

283
00:22:59.894 --> 00:23:00.965
"Yes"?

284
00:23:01.104 --> 00:23:03.634
You know, if you ever get bored of being alone...

