00:23:08.945 --> 00:23:12.344
I feel so refreshed. Why did I wait so long?

286
00:23:13.475 --> 00:23:15.245
You should be careful.

287
00:23:15.515 --> 00:23:18.285
Don't let any water get into your eyes.

288
00:23:19.055 --> 00:23:20.584
Get me the hair dryer.

289
00:23:21.255 --> 00:23:22.424
Where is it?

290
00:23:25.255 --> 00:23:26.894
It pays to live long.

291
00:23:27.094 --> 00:23:28.795
What a luxury this is.

292
00:23:35.434 --> 00:23:36.604
Hello?

293
00:23:38.975 --> 00:23:40.035
Hello?

294
00:23:43.104 --> 00:23:44.315
Ho Sung.

295
00:23:46.574 --> 00:23:47.684
Ho Sung?

296
00:23:53.815 --> 00:23:55.455
Yes, Mom.

297
00:23:55.455 --> 00:23:57.824
Hello, my daughter.

298
00:23:59.124 --> 00:24:00.354
Did you eat dinner?

299
00:24:01.725 --> 00:24:02.965
Yes, I did.

300
00:24:03.924 --> 00:24:05.195
What about you?

301
00:24:05.934 --> 00:24:09.735
- How are you feeling? - I'm fine. I'm all better now.

302
00:24:09.735 --> 00:24:13.134
