306
00:24:21.584 --> 00:24:23.945
Boil barley tea to keep your body warm.

307
00:24:24.144 --> 00:24:26.584
You always have a cold in winter.

308
00:24:27.384 --> 00:24:29.584
Turn on the heating high.

309
00:24:31.094 --> 00:24:33.354
Okay. Yes.

310
00:24:39.495 --> 00:24:42.805
(My Cosmos, My Eternal Flower)

311
00:24:44.275 --> 00:24:46.634
Ho Sung kept this all along.

312
00:24:53.344 --> 00:24:54.745
Ji Won.

313
00:24:55.384 --> 00:24:58.584
Do you know the very first flower the universe created?

314
00:25:00.924 --> 00:25:03.285
- Cosmos? - Yes.

315
00:25:04.725 --> 00:25:07.795
It's imperfect because it was the first flower to be created,

316
00:25:07.995 --> 00:25:09.795
but it's the most loved one.

317
00:25:10.424 --> 00:25:14.505
That's why she called herself my mom's cosmos.

318
00:25:17.104 --> 00:25:18.334
Jin Jin.

319
00:25:22.374 --> 00:25:24.574
Do you know what the meaning of cosmos is?

320
00:25:26.945 --> 00:25:28.545
Not just any meaning.

321
00:25:29.515 --> 00:25:31.255
The one your sister made.

322
00:25:36.184 --> 00:25:37.525
I love you.

323
00:26:10.725 --> 00:26:12.195
- Here you go. - Thanks.

324
00:26:13.695 --> 00:26:15.525
The meeting is next Monday.

325
00:26:15.525 --> 00:26:17.634
I'll be there for the fitting.

326
00:26:17.634 --> 00:26:20.094
