328
00:26:22.705 --> 00:26:26.634
Her hair is a problem. It needs to be braided and put in a bun.

329
00:26:26.634 --> 00:26:28.344
I already scheduled a meeting with hairstylists.

330
00:26:29.604 --> 00:26:30.775
But Jin Jin,

