351
00:27:27.195 --> 00:27:28.664
This is Bella.

352
00:27:30.934 --> 00:27:32.574
I'm in Korea.

353
00:27:33.735 --> 00:27:35.275
Let's meet.

354
00:27:37.975 --> 00:27:39.275
Here he comes.

355
00:27:54.025 --> 00:27:56.424
Hi. We look forward to working with you.

356
00:27:56.424 --> 00:27:59.265
All right. He's the new addition to our building and the bodyguard.

